title: Hi 5 snow party
creator_credit: Kids Like Us, Nine Films and Television, Nine Network (Australia), Posie Graeme-Evans, Helena Harris and Ian Munro
brief_description: The Hi5 gang - Tim Harding, Nathan Foley, Kathleen De Leon, Kellie Hoggart and Charli Robinson have lots of fun together, singing, dancing, telling stories and discovering how and why things happen. Suitable for lower primary school children.
